ontology_name: This field is used for set the ontology name (Mandatory)
trait: If the term is part of a subontology, you can set the subontology name here (optional)
url: If the term has a URL for reference you can set here (Optional)
term_es: If the term has translates, the user can add extra columns in this CSV file for each one. The column name must be the reserved word "term_" and the language code in ISO 639-1. Example: if the user add column for spanish language the column name is "term_es"
